      <h3>Objective</h3>
      <p>
        To build a functional
        <strong>social platform</strong>
        on the
        <strong>Noroff API</strong>
        with a focus on clean JavaScript architecture, authentication, and core features like posts,
        profiles, search, and follow. This was primarily a
