        <strong>API-driven UI</strong>
        and
        <strong>authentication flows</strong>. This project was primarily code focused (no dedicated
        UI design phase), so my main goal was to build a clean, predictable experience through solid
        structure, form validation/feedback, and consistent state handling.
      </p>
